  <span class="font-mono text-[0.58rem] text-[var(--accent)] tracking-wide">made with that iconic duck green</span>
  <span class="font-mono text-[0.58rem] text-[var(--gray-faint)] tracking-wide">chaulagainrupak.com.np</span>
